	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Just to be clear, there are 8 different palettes, not 2. 4 for BG and 4 for Sprites.
<br />
<br />There are 3 unique colors to each palette, since the first color for each one is the same.
<br />
<br />So 3 * 8 + 1 = 25 is more like it.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


